longBusinessSummary: Invech Holdings, Inc. manufactures and sells OEM and ODM products under Hello Kitty, Disney, MonsterHigh, and Angry Birds brands names in the People's Republic of China. It offers Bluetooth and USB speakers, keyboards, mouse and sleeves combo, mouse pad, and USB hub and cooling pad. The company was formerly known as Mega Win Investments, Inc. and changed its name to Invech Holdings, Inc. in August 2018. Invech Holdings, Inc. is based in Dongguan, the People's Republic of China.
